Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.21,0:00:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}For the first time, I didn't watch the charts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The bot made three trades.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.25,0:00:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I checked once.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.78,0:00:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I can't code.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}9 years in crypto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.55,0:00:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}AI trades my thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.76,0:00:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.83,0:00:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That day I spent rewriting the website.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.65,0:00:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Reframed every line from trading product to social experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Meanwhile, the bot made three trades on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.93,0:00:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Net down about a dollar eighty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I looked once.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.76,0:00:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Then closed the tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Not because I didn't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.85,0:00:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Because I'd finally built something I could stop policing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.39,0:00:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The real test of any system you build is — can you stop watching it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If you can't, you didn't build a system.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.72,0:00:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You built a second job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.57,0:00:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Most people can't tell the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.01,0:00:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That was the first day I rented my attention back from the bot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:00:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It was cheaper than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 10 tomorrow — Twitter took my account without warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.79,0:01:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Follow along.
